-- Carbon Capture Projects, Green Investment Bank Funded by U.K. Treasury
-- B y   R o b e r t   H u t t o n
-- 2010-10-20T11:32:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/carbon-capture-projects-green-investment-bank-funded-by-u-k-treasury.html
U.K. Prime Minister David Cameron
said the government will press ahead with carbon capture and
wind-power projects as part of its environmental policies.  “The carbon capture and storage projects -- they’re going
ahead,” he said in Parliament in London today. “The wind-power
projects -- they’re going ahead. The Green Investment Bank -- we
will put money into it.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
